# 🏆 FIFA World Cup 2026 - Player Performance Analysis 

Data-driven insights from **54,600 players** across **32 teams** at FIFA World Cup 2026. Comprehensive analysis of player performance, team strength, and positional effectiveness.

---

## 📊 Quick Overview

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| **Total Players** | 54,600 |
| **Teams** | 32 Nations |
| **Data Attributes** | 75 Columns |
| **Duplicates** | 0 ✅ |
| **Data Quality** | 100% |

---

## 📂 What's Inside?

```
📁 Dataset Includes:
├── Player Information (Name, Age, Nationality, Jersey #)
├── Physical Attributes (Height, Weight, Preferred Foot)
├── Tournament Stats (Goals, Assists, Minutes, Ratings)
├── Performance Metrics (Creativity, Consistency, Pressure Resistance)
└── Team Comparisons & Rankings
```

---

## 🔍 Analysis Covered

✅ **Data Exploration & Validation**
- Complete data structure analysis
- Duplicate detection & missing values check
- Data type validation

✅ **Descriptive Statistics**
- Player age, height, weight distributions
- Performance metric summaries

✅ **Position Distribution**
- Goalkeeper, Defender, Midfielder, Forward breakdowns
- Squad composition insights

✅ **Team Performance**
- Average tournament ratings by team
- Team strength comparison
- Performance rankings

---

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Requirements
```bash
Python 3.7+
Jupyter Notebook
```

### Installation
```bash
# Clone repo
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/fifa-worldcup-analysis.git
cd fifa-worldcup-analysis

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run Jupyter
jupyter notebook
```

### Open & Run
Open `FIFA_WORLDCUP_ANALYSIS-checkpoint.ipynb` in Jupyter and run all cells.

---

## 📈 Key Findings

### 1️⃣ Player Distribution
Shows which positions have the highest representation across all 32 teams.

### 2️⃣ Team Strength
Teams with **higher average ratings** performed better overall, while lower-rated teams showed weaker tournament performance.

### 3️⃣ Data Quality
- ✅ No duplicate records
- ✅ Proper data types
- ✅ Valid player information
- ✅ Complete tournament statistics

